          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ".R race cars to consumers. However, that won’t happen until the 2024 racing season begins. Before anyone reads this wrong, let’s just clarify: this won’t be a homologation, street-legal model. Yeah, that would be cool if Chevrolet made a Corvette Z06 GT3 in the vein of the Porsche 911 GT3, but for now that’s not happening.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
